Update or delete multiple secrets from multiple repositories

Usage:
  secrethub bulk init [CONFIG]
  secrethub bulk save [CONFIG --clean]
  secrethub bulk clean [CONFIG]
  secrethub bulk list [CONFIG]
  secrethub bulk (-h|--help)

Commands:
  init
    Create a sample configuration file in the current directory

  save
    Save multiple secrets to multiple repositories

  clean
    Delete secrets from multiple repositories unless they are specified
    in the config file

  list
    Show all secrets in all repositories

Options:
  -c, --clean
    Also delete any other secret not defined in the config file

  -h --help
    Show this help

Parameters:
  CONFIG
    Path to the configuration file

Examples:
  secrethub bulk init
  secrethub bulk clean
  secrethub bulk update mysecrets.yml
  secrethub bulk update --clean
